Summary: Object that alternates red and green lights.
divs: Sighting DetailsI first noticed the object as I went out to the car to get some work papers. Theobject seemed to alternate red and green lights. I observed other stars andaircraft at the same time but nothing matched the alternating changes in red andgreen lights. The object seems to be on the same plane as another star but thisobject is closer compared to the stars far off appearence.
